Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet…flowers…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:08.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you read this letter,\NI doubt that I’ll be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So to you, my most trusted one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll write everything that\NI have uncovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I first read\Nthe captain’s letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t believe my eyes.\NI couldn’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:30.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it is true…\NI’ll believe the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:35.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen…\NThe one who killed you is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can faint from hunger…\Nyou have it, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:13.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Gin Ichimaru.\NPleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gin… What a strange name…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You awake, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing in\Nmy room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:35.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The office isn’t your room!\NIf you’re awake, take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:43.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because you went and took\Nall the paperwork for Squad 5’s takeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet. You finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all?\NThere was so much more…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:04:01.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been asleep a long time,\Nhaven’t I…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your classmate is fighting\Nwith your junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My classmate, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:23.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really suspect Gin…\NCaptain Ichimaru was the one who…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:25.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:29.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kokichiro Takezoe,\NSquad 10, 7th Seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are Captain Hitsugaya and\NLieutenant Matsumoto here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:36.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An urgent message from\Nthe guard stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:48.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai, Lieutenant Hinamori,\Nand Lieutenant Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,have vanished from their cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When Lieutenant Hinamori called,\Nand I turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:06.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a blinding white light,\Nand I awoke in this state…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have…no excuse for it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hakufuku…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hakufuku…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori is a master\Nof the Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we truly wished to restrain her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we should have sealed\Nher Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:31.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn’t done because\Nno one expected her to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like she was under\Na death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s only one reason…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:49.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go back without me.\NI’m going to save Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori, don’t do anything rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He now maintains his stance,\Neven when his sword breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Ichigo, the deadline is near…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s fifty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. I almost had him…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment of impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he adjusted to the enemy’s speed\Nand deflected the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, without slowing down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he shifted instantaneously\Nto counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, he no longer relies on\Nthe power of Zangetsu, his weapon…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s absorbing it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With fearsome speed…\NAt a fearsome level…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara, you were right.\NThe boy is truly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:47.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Boss,\Nhave you caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:51.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, some pretty girl is\Nprobably talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that’s such a cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…! That will never do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:02.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good remedy for colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This expired two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nicely aged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say “Aah…”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Haah? N-No! Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Drink, drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? Ah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta…I gotta save Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Rukia Kuchiki\Nhave to be executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they keep\Nmoving up the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:49.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I was investigating,\NI came upon the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know it.\NIn my place…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been fighting\Nfor over five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with this single sword…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s nearing the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:08.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lay down your sword, Ichigo.\NThe first day is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:35.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t tell it was night, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:39.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t tell time here,\Nso you sure get disoriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:51.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’s with this hot spring?!\NMy scar’s healing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:52.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would it work if I drank it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How’s the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,[Great! The water’s great]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll join you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty’s wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you take off\Nyour pants first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:25.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always react exactly\Nas expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!\NYou makin’ fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:32.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Agh! Don’t come in! N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no problem now,\Nis there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you a little disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna drown you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:55.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place looks a lot\Nlike that place…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Training Ground\Nunder Urahara’s Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That place was modeled\Nafter this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:13.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When Kisuke and I were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we secretly built it as\Nour secret play ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This hu-ge space…secretly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s an old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When we were kids,\Nwe played here almost every day…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After he joined\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:40.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I joined the Stealth Force,\Nwe honed our skills here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute, Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why sit cross-legged?!\NDon’t sit like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. I never get tired\Nof that reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me more about\Nthe old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So he was a Soul Reaper, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He knew so much about Soul Society\Nand he had a zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:10.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Yoruichi.\NWho is he, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s the former captain of Squad 12
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He even founded and served
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:23.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as the first chief of the Department\Nof Research and Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!\NDidn’t know he was that important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:42.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good stomach medicine\Nthat works wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll dig it out from the back yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re together,\Nas I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:29.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only Kira’s cell was unlocked\Nfrom the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:34.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted it to be a secret,\Nweren’t you a little careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Ichimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:40.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that’s a funny thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:45.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it on purpose,\Nso you’d know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a good thing\NI got here before Hinamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:56.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before she gets here,\NI’ll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At last…I’ve found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:17.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hinamori!\NYou’re no match for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll handle this. Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:29.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To avenge…Captain Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill the Captain…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from this letter left\Nby the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori, the true purpose\Nfor this execution
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is not to kill Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:58.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This execution was contrived\Nin order to steal a certain object.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:04.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Its true objective is…\NThe Sokyoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Sokyoku’s seal is\Nbroken only for an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:14.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In its blade lies the destructive power\Nof a million zanpaku-tô.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It also possesses\Nthe defensive ability
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to block equally powerful\Nzanpaku-to, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:27.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, when a Soul Reaper\Nis crucified and stabbed with Sokyoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:32.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,its power grows dozens\Nof times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who plotted this execution\Nplans to use this power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy not only the Seireitei,\Nbut Soul Society itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the name of this vile person is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro…Hitsugaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The letter goes on to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve called him out to\Nthe Sacred Eastern Wall tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:11.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must stop his plan somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’m resolved to fight him\Nif he won’t desist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if I should die…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:24.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori, won’t you carry out\Nmy wishes and avenge him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final request…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:32.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not as the captain of Squad 5…\Nbut as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I ask this…of you…!”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Think carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies, he wants you\Nto fight instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think\NAizen would say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Aizen I know was\Nnever stupid enough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to face unbeatable odds alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he was no coward that makes\Nhis men bail him out either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…But that’s what the letter said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In Captain Aizen’s handwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:20.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t want to believe it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s what\NCaptain Aizen said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:33.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:41.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know…\Nwhat to do anymore…Shiro-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:53.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No good. She’s too upset\Nto think rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:57.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Aizen would never write\Na letter like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must’ve forged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that Hinamori and\NI would kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:20.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This, too…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was this all your doing, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:50.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. That was cruel,\NSquad 10 Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:57.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was hurt and so desperate.\NWhy hit her so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:05.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The warning certainly came…\Nat a convenient time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:10.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:16.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forget what you\Nsaid back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop and listen to\Nthe last alarm, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon you won’t be able to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:34.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Aizen wasn’t enough for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You even had to hurt\NHinamori this bad…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:47.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To make her grip her sword\Nso hard that her hands bled…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:50.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:02.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever made Hinamori bleed,\NI’d kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That will never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:20.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your sword in a place like this\Nand I’ll be forced to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:44.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:55.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:17.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:28.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:35.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, this time for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:38.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a safe,\Nnutritional supplement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no… I’m all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the latest Chinese medicine\Nadvertised in the evening paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t trust that…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:47.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It works on a variety of ailments!